PEARL 2: Tríada\\Nde Virchow 201","guid":"","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"### Componentes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"- Estasis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"- Inmovilidad: post-ACV, viajes aéreos >5-6 horas","guid":"JkPi9Ty_-zkSAx2DP0DcLg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"17","text":"- Flujo lento: insuficiencia cardíaca","guid":"lH8fmkORPe1n3TO1x5r6zQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"17","text":"- Obstrucción vascular: tumor, embarazo, anomalías anatómicas","guid":"LJ1WJCdVB59KhKk4vYLPsw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"17","text":"- Hiperviscosidad: policitemia, leucemia, Waldenstrom","guid":"UmnVLTSKWuH8SXiQave1lQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"16","text":"- Lesión\\Nendotelial","guid":"I3r2_GrjWSSyBmV_DyTYgw","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"- Espontánea: bacteriemia, infecciones de piel/tejidos blandos, cicatrices","guid":"79ongfnhtB6-wP6mpFyvPA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"- Iatrogénica: catéteres, radioterapia","guid":"_bRIKHiFNFRgemnsZg5hWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"16","text":"- Estado\\Nhipercoagulable","guid":"Xmo6EXB8WJce9Uj-2iAe_g","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"- Causas hematológicas primarias: trombofilias hereditarias, SAAF","guid":"DOlpGT2sXoT0xj3b1kWntA","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"- Secundarias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"- Aumento de factores protrombóticos: embarazo, ACO, estados estrogénicos","guid":"P2Jfqll6zlMJi8EcftNESQ","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"- Pérdida de anticoagulantes naturales: cirrosis, síndrome nefrótico","guid":"c6HqyJCI4fFicRsH56yTng","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"- Otros: hemoglobinuria paroxística nocturna, neoplasias mieloproliferativas","guid":"Oy-LvKCBUyWOMu_yjCXb0g","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"## PEARL 3: Pruebas de trombofilia hereditaria,\\Nparte 1: deficiencias proteicas","guid":"VlYSBgpOyw55hBEdWwW_jw","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"### Tipos de trombofilias\\Nprimarias","guid":"gc1Hcps9umYfn3GHelj_dg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"- Trombofilias hereditarias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"- Trombofilias adquiridas (SAAF)","guid":"5NckLG2vGwvQreVtpDNT7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"### Deficiencias\\Nproteicas hereditarias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"- Deficiencia de\\Nantitrombina III\\N(ATIII)","guid":"Y-BE2ZtuYiW5OHI6wmPCxw","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"- Anticoagulante natural que reduce actividad de la cascada de coagulación","guid":"TsYSmCrOCX4Am8V7WC-wRQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"- Heparina actúa a través de ATIII","guid":"ya_ajAqiZGlgYdxo87j86w","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"- Deficiencias de\\Nproteína C y S","guid":"","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"- Previenen coágulos inhibiendo factores V y VIII","guid":"Pkq98wkPLT0eq2tju9DecA","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"- Síntesis dependiente de vitamina K","guid":"cwjQYAduzVvukFYpWvOXkQ","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"- Warfarina crea deficiencia temporal → estado protrombótico inicial","guid":"nnoedj5fmeNEBYO0ySdrZg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"31","text":"### Problemas en la\\Ninterpretación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"- Pueden imitar falsamente\\Ndeficiencia heredada","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"- Anticoagulación con heparina o warfarina","guid":"7ZJU_fwoooMX6SabFOkOWA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"- Gran carga de coágulos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"- Estados de alto estrógeno","guid":"zfOrRKT3WHxx9qzxLbZmew","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"- Síndrome nefrótico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"44","text":"- Inflamación aguda","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"43","text":"- Resultados \"bajos\"\\Npueden ser","guid":"A3wyVw1cPqkYtfNx5QaFGg","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"- Deficiencia verdadera hereditaria","guid":"xcnVFkYJCMPi6uNF_tOn2Q","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"- Estado deficiente temporal (secundario)","guid":"8aLDtfcEUz1d2yQFLT3apw","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"- Deficiencia falsa (artefacto por anticoagulantes)","guid":"jqM00nk9_wiu-rhkXYCI2g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"## PEARL 4: Pruebas de trombofilia hereditaria,\\Nparte 2: mutaciones protrombóticas","guid":"uLiN6_qzi0dubSKJZay8BQ","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"### Mutaciones genéticas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"- Factor V Leiden","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"- Protrombina G20210A","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"### Ventajas de\\Npruebas genéticas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- No afectadas por estado de salud actual","guid":"OLKbN07DT7xcjG9curMx7g","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"- No afectadas por carga de coágulos","guid":"22kBTvMqxXStfFl9PprK1g","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"- No afectadas por anticoagulación","guid":"D5QMxx0O_VAppmHZkk5LNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"54","text":"### Limitaciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"- Factor V Leiden heterocigótico es común pero con penetrancia variable","guid":"DsRg7m6-sGab-Ou0x1nLgQ","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"- Mayoría de pacientes con FVL heterocigótico no desarrollan coágulos","guid":"VCcae9MBBcQMEjUGCeJMlA","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"- FVL homocigótico no garantiza desarrollo de coágulos","guid":"DKYmSZnopDo5kIRwvGQ2zQ","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"- Historia familiar es más importante que resultados de pruebas","guid":"Fwei7bT76k7GuveHNGX8bQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"62","text":"- Edad >60 es factor de riesgo (irreversible)","guid":"MOGS6p-r60HpNhx9UpBi-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"54","text":"### Cuándo\\Nconsiderar pruebas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"- Paciente joven con coágulo inexplicable y fuerte historia familiar (<60 años)","guid":"uMTBXHGf6P_c1IB4_OKUyw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"- Paciente con coágulo y posible trastorno hereditario + hijo planeando embarazo o ACO","guid":"9OXKZDpDbahgdfciLOPUKQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"- Cuando el paciente se beneficiaría de entender mejor su condición","guid":"QR0BjxLR8kRj7HrQUxTS2Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"## PEARL 5: Recapitulación\\Ny aplicaciones","guid":"7-BsHG5LTtyEFrFM9UGnLQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"### Caso 1:\\NHombre de 48\\Naños","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"- Esguince de tobillo + 2 días inmovilidad → DVT y EP subsegmental","guid":"MM772gnoXG4sYv5G5gG1LA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"- Historia familiar: madre con EP no provocado a los 50, hermana con coágulo post-parto","guid":"22-ZVfynPcl_3FwKFJKPRw","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"- Tipo de coágulo: provocado-reversible con historia familiar preocupante","guid":"VzqKLfFWnt7ay-uoOLfIlQ","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"- Pruebas recomendadas: Factor V Leiden, protrombina G20210A","guid":"6iN9skdeyPc4Lp1vjwAWSA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"- No enviar pruebas de deficiencia proteica durante anticoagulación","guid":"EGSiCSP_z5VyyNrtVFix6w","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"73","text":"- Manejo: anticoagulación mínimo 3 meses + seguimiento por Hematología","guid":"HrIvO4K7f59UMiR9lSdF8g","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"72","text":"### Caso 2:\\NMujer de 40 años","guid":"","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"- DVT/EP tras esguince, tía con DVT a los 70 años","guid":"EjxxZPSnHrYistLOxqly0g","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"- Completó 3 meses de DOAC","guid":"KvkMBsnm6Y7YDiTMzpz__g","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"- Hija de 16 años considerando ACO","guid":"kX_DQbFkSqUzvydWDevh4A","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"80","text":"- Tipo de coágulo: provocado-reversible con historia familiar no convincente","guid":"Gn-58o8oHB_m2NDIALOdbw","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"80","text":"- Pruebas posibles: todas (ya no está anticoagulada)","guid":"GtUUa0hVTlZqVjfq_N5aIA","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"80","text":"- Manejo: considerar pruebas para informar decisiones sobre ACO de la hija","guid":"qQp4wSln507OqxOba95cyg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":86,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Nefrología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Nefrología","filename":"Perlas. Abordaje de hipercoagulabilidad-2025-1","id":"map_1329","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Perlas. Abordaje de hipercoagulabilidad-2025-1"}